# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 月点 (Moondot) — Server environment variables
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your actual values.
# .env.local is git-ignored — never commit secrets.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# OpenAI API key (required for real model calls)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Model to use for structured outputs (defaults to gpt-4.1-mini)
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4.1-mini

# Optional base URL for OpenAI-compatible proxies
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=

# Optional User-Agent override for OpenAI-compatible proxies that require it.
# For micuapi Codex/Responses compatibility:
#   OPENAI_MODEL should be a model name such as gpt-5.4, not the group name vip_2.
#   OPENAI_BASE_URL should be https://www.micuapi.ai/v1.
#   OPENAI_USER_AGENT should follow the value documented at:
# https://docs.micuapi.ai/external-compat
# OPENAI_USER_AGENT=
